name: Outter Finance
description: Outter Finance is a decentralized financial asset built on the Binance Smart Chain and accessible through the PancakeSwap platform. It introduces a unique advanced protocol that combines auto-staking and a rewards system to provide token holders with recurring income and appreciation. By simply holding the $OUT tokens, users can passively earn compound interest through the auto-staking mechanism, contributing to their daily returns. The protocol implements an annual APY model, ensuring that token holders benefit from increased value over time.
